blog.name: dramaphan
blog.title: Yo I Comment On The Drama When Shit Hits The Fan
blog.description:
Phandom drama? It's more likely than you think.

.

My ask box is always open if you need a place to be dramatic, share theories, conspiracies, opinions, or general grievances. Fire away, my babies. Nothing is off limits. (Except for the things that are.)

.

Icon by phanniephobic, header by cinnamonnutlester

body:
Google feud review:

-wtf I thought this was a gaming video why are they talking about robots


-like seriously we’re two minutes into the video now and they’ve just flapped about, get on with it lads.


-“I tried the iced Capp” *shows photo of an iced coffee*


-“should I pierce my ladydoor” FUCK


-Phil have you ever seen someone with pierced nipples you gotta get them both or else it looks weird and lopsided.


-“should we do a mukbang instead of this video?” I mean you’ve barely played any game so what the hell, why not.


-“men can be milked.” Nobody explain this to me. I would rather die never knowing what the fuck he means.


-“how to get out of bed” alright Dan take it back a notch


-“is anyone else leaving one direction?” Yeah all of them.


-They aren’t even trying anymore And I think Dan’s got pizza grease pooled around his brain or something.


-they’re fucking dabbing again unsubscribed bye.


-“I’m going to kill you to death” can I be next, please?


-Phil is now stress-spanking Lion idk how to feel.


Conclusion: this video was a hot mess from start to finish and if I see a single bit of bed discourse instead of the countless other things said in this video I will riot.
